<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .date-range {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo-container img {
            max-width: 200px;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        {{#if mailLogoUrl}}
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="{{mailLogoUrl}}" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        <h2>Field Service Job Report</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello Team,</p>

        <p>Please find attached the Field Service job report for the following period:</p>

        <div class="date-range">
            <strong>Report Period:</strong> {{monthStart}} to {{monthEnd}}
        </div>

        <p>The attached CSV file contains detailed information about all scheduled field service jobs during this period.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions or need clarification, please reach out to the operations team.</p>

        {{#if recipientCount}}
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #999; margin-top: 20px;">
            This report was sent to {{recipientCount}} recipient(s).
        </p>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="footer">
            {{#if mailDisclaimerText}}
            {{{mailDisclaimerText}}}
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
